    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Apathy/Inertia
---
The force that opposes determination is inertia. Inertia is not a static
thing; it is a dynamic force. Like any force, it tends to magnify itself
and gain momentum until or unless it is superseded by another force
stronger than itself.
